.PP
SIGINT (CTRL+C) prints current clock\-drift (audio\-clock \- system\-clock).
SIGQUIT (CTRL+\e) terminates the program.
SIGHUP initialize a re\-sync to system clock (unless \fB\-t\fR is given).
